    MockitoJUnitRunner
    public static class MockitoJUnitRunner.Strict
extends MockitoJUnitRunner
    Detects unused stubs and reports them as failures. Default behavior in Mockito 2.x. To improve productivity and quality of tests please consider newer API, the MockitoJUnitRunner.StrictStubs.

    For more information on detecting unused stubs, see UnnecessaryStubbingException. For more information on stubbing argument mismatch warnings see MockitoHint.

    Since:
    2.1.0
